      + [periphery] is retry mechanism, prompt delivery, and nearby validation signals
      + [correlations] is correlation between loop tick timing, retry success, and prompt appearance
      + [causal_hypotheses] is hypothesis only, not proof, that retry timing may relate to later prompt display
      + [outside] is no direct proof of causation, hidden activation access, or broad competence
      + [caution] is keep correlation separate from evidence until logs support a causal claim
      + [next_step] is compare loop tick logs, prompt events, and validator records before claiming causation

    Final check before answering:
